Nigerian Instagram comedian, Craze Crown’s his fiancee, Jojo has shared postpartum images of her body 7 weeks after the birth of their first child, GIA. She did this to encourage other women, stating that they should always remember what their body went through for nine months and be proud, also adding that “Don’t stress over post baby body, instead love yourself, your marks, the pigmentation and your baby” Taking to her personal Instagram handle, she shared the photos with the caption; “7 weeks postpartum and thought to share where I’m at postbaby. It sure is incredible what the woman body can do and I’m so grateful!. For all mothers out there, always remember what your body went through for nine months and be proud. Don’t stress over post baby body, instead love yourself, your marks, the pigmentation and your baby because you are beautiful just the way you are”